(night time:11.5) A highly detailed, cinematic exterior (night shot:9.25) of a modern one-storey commercial building, masterpiece quality. The building has a flat concrete roof with a low-profile mechanical unit centered at the top. The symmetrical facade is divided into six equal storefronts:

The four central sections are clad in textured sandstone with large, dark blue reflective glass panels, revealing subtle glimpses of illuminated interiors.

The leftmost section is made of (gray basalt:2) with a small rectangular opening near the top left.

The rightmost section is finished in rough white stucco, visibly textured.

Each storefront is marked at the top by a sign with the word “store” inside in bold white letters. A clean horizontal (white stucco band:2) runs across all six sections, providing visual continuity and it's the same finish as the rightmost section. The base of each section features dark blue reflective glass panels that offer transparent views into the softly lit interiors, emphasizing interior light glow and night ambiance.

The smooth, light-colored concrete ground in front of the building reflects ambient light.

In the foreground, a single blurry man walks past, adding scale and movement. In the background, other modern buildings of beige and grey tones complete the urban nighttime setting.

nodes.title: main night shot render
widgets_values:
GHIBSKY style, A masterpiece night exterior shot photo of a modern administrative building with a distinctive, angular architectural style. The structure rises three stories, with a visually prominent ground floor. Its facade is composed of alternating vertical strips of greenish glass and light sandstone cladding, forming a grid-like rhythm. The rough texture of the sandstone is dramatically highlighted by architectural uplighting embedded into the facade, casting elongated shadows and emphasizing surface depth.

A Ferrari cruises by on the street in motion blur, while a few people walk nearby, contributing to the building’s dynamic urban atmosphere. A no-entry traffic sign is visible on the corner, enhancing realism. The surrounding scene includes small landscaped trees, low curbs, and sidewalks. Above, the night sky is clear and filled with stars, while subtle purple-orange dusk tones hint at residual twilight beyond the horizon.

The building bears the sign “NAMAA” in sleek uppercase letters at the roof edge, adding identity and purpose to the scene.
